- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with action localization using visual data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses machine learning techniques to learn spatio-temporal action detectors. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves learning from data to improve performance. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing videos. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves tracking humans in videos, which could have applications in robotics.
